The 2019 MyBroadband Conference and Expo will take place on 17 October 2019 at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Gauteng. It is the premier ICT event in South Africa and the meeting place for the country’s IT and telecoms community. Every year SA’s top telecoms and IT companies partner with MyBroadband to showcase their products and services and interact with local IT decision-makers. It is well-known that IT executives and business owners attend the conference to see what is on offer and make purchasing decisions based on this information. All conference delegates also receive a voucher booklet with special deals on telecommunications and IT products for the business market from exhibitors. Registrations for the 2019 MyBroadband Conference has now opened with a big special on early-bird tickets. It should be noted that only 200 of these special tickets are available. The tickets cover all aspects of the event, including access to the expo and conference, lunch, and refreshments.